            {
              "block_type": "text",
              "display_order": 1,
              "content_text": "Kevin was asked to work out $2\\frac{1}{3} \\times \\frac{5}{8}$\n\nHere is his working and his answer.\n\n$2\\frac{1}{3} \\times \\frac{5}{8} = \\frac{7}{3} \\times \\frac{5}{8} = \\frac{35}{24} = 1\\frac{9}{24}$\n\nKevin's answer is wrong.\n\nWhat mistake has Kevin made?",
              "diagram_description": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
