              "content_text": null,
              "diagram_description": "L-shaped floor plan with outer dimensions 10m width and 8m height. A rectangular section is cut out from the bottom right, leaving a 6m wide section at the bottom. The right side shows 5m height for the upper portion."
            },
            {
              "block_type": "text",
              "display_order": 3,
              "content_text": "Petra is going to cover the floor with paint.\n\nPetra has 3 tins of paint.\nThere are 2.5 litres of paint in each tin.\n\nPetra thinks 1 litre of paint will cover $10\\text{m}^2$ of floor.",
              "diagram_description": null
